rows.field_385332: I'd love to be able to sign on with my face ID or stay signed in for longer.
I'd be very interested to be able to use a foreign bank as well to retrieve my balance.
Customer service was a bit challenging to get through to. Improving customer service would make a difference in my experience.
A change in bold font would be helpful.
Would give full 5 stars if I was able to sign on with face ID.
Having a dark theme or a customizable team as an option would take this to 5 stars across the board for me.

rows.field_379930: The background display is black, and the text color is changed to white.
Add a bank outside of the country as one of the banks on the account.
If the application is on an iPhone, allow face ID to sign the customer into the application.
Add a specific priority level to each purchase.
Allows you to select a budget advisor of the 10 available.
Allows you to link to 3rd party payment apps to detect payments.
Allows you to set deadlines for certain financial goals.

rows.field_379928: Link to a variety of  bank account
rows.field_379930: The app can be linked to individual bank accounts.
The automated budget can be manually adjusted.
Alarms can be configured to notify the customer when they are close to crossing their budget.
